{"tid":2437051,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"承辦商處理檢測結果時樣本瓶編號有錯　涉逾百名市民","createTime":"2021-03-07T15:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T15:39:17.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"48c0db4323ab4c86a2f56fbf52f94483c208ba8c","tid":2437051,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:18:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579259-20210307.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579259-20210307.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058v5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=849784ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579259-20210307.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a55fbc61\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579259-20210307.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n醫管局表示，有新冠病毒檢測化驗承辦商，處理檢測結果時樣本瓶編號出錯，令過百名巿民收到的檢測結果短訊載有錯誤編號，有關市民因而未能登入政府的電子檢測紀錄系統下載紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局表示，事件涉及103名市民，他們曾於本月2日在普通科門診診所交回樣本瓶，經檢測後所有結果為陰性。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局又說，承辦商確認有關錯誤不涉及個人資料和私隱，亦沒有影響檢測結果，醫管局已要求承辦商立即通知受影響市民及發出更正電話短訊，並責成承辦商全面檢視系統及修正錯誤，防止再發生類似事件。"},{"pid":"e7a8dc9facab768f2250dd583ae6b241759687a4","tid":2437051,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07fd89640ee489c66f376acc8e7d410ffb0bd40","tid":2437051,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:22:48.000Z","msg":"今次要唔要拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe59d0c29810b7e124e0d217ebbd74c0ec740b8","tid":2437051,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"依家香港既 NEWSPEAK：<br />\n<br />\n錯 =&gt; 有偏差<br />\n<br />\n錯到離譜 =&gt; 唔理想<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}